{"root":{"data":{"text":"微波光子成像干扰一体化技术研究"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp0tfqfn4s","created":1531797858298,"text":"研究背景和意义","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp15m8zmog","created":1531797884814,"text":"研究背景","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxqhw1j94w","created":1773128896555,"text":"在现代战争中，无人机的广泛应用给雷达探测带来了新的挑战。一方面，无人机的雷达散射截面积远远小于舰船坦克等，这大大提高了雷达识别无人机的难度；另一方面，无人机往往数量繁多，还采用集群技术协同作战，如果想要精准探测不同的无人机，这就对于雷达分辨率提出了很高的要求。此外，现代战场上，雷达作为敌方无人机攻击的重要目标，也需要具有一定的自保能力。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp16beu2w4","created":1531797886335,"text":"存在的问题","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxrcuisruo","created":1773128963943,"text":"得益于集成电路和相控阵的发展等，传统电域探测干扰一体化程度高，但是由于电子瓶颈的限制，其难以实现高频宽带信号的高保真储存和高响应速度"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp16p7fl4o","created":1531797887169,"text":"研究的必要性","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0vi3wjs4","created":1531797862795,"text":"2. 阶段工作总结","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp17ohlswk","created":1531797889303,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18cjbegw","created":1531797890757,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18qmdhs8","created":1531797891608,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp28g7gco4","created":1531797969343,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0w7fnc0k","created":1531797864327,"text":"3. 亮点与不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":47,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp19f2yo84","created":1531797893087,"text":"1. 工作亮点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp19rtkeo8","created":1531797893858,"text":"2. 工作不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0wnpf808","created":1531797865311,"text":"4. 阶段工作规划","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1apwzq8k","created":1531797895919,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1b1h3z4g","created":1531797896618,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1bd2qds8","created":1531797897320,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1brn0xcs","created":1531797898200,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0xg6s1s0","created":1531797867033,"text":"5. 改进建议","layout_right_offset":{"x":61,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1ccip1s8","created":1531797899463,"text":"1. 对公司","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1d52ua04","created":1531797901190,"text":"2. 对部门","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-red-compat","version":"1.4.43"}